<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New Client Introduction</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f3f4f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f2937;">
    <div style="padding: 32px 16px;">
      <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0;">
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);">
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
              <tr>
                <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff 0%, #f0f9ff 100%); padding: 28px 32px;">
                  <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="width: 72px; vertical-align: top;">
                        {{advisorLogoBlock}}
                      </td>
                      <td style="padding-left: 16px;">
                        <p style="margin: 0; color: #6366f1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;">Advisor Match</p>
                        <h1 style="margin: 8px 0 6px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">{{advisorCompanyName}}</h1>
                        <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563;">Primary contact: <strong style="color: #111827;">{{advisorName}}</strong></p>
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">{{advisorYearsExperience}} years experience · {{advisorNumberOfTransactions}} closed deals</p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 28px 32px;">
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1f2937;">
                    Hi {{advisorName}},<br /><br />
                    We're excited to introduce you to <strong>{{sellerCompany}}</strong>, a seller operating in {{sellerIndustry}} across {{sellerGeography}}. {{sellerName}} is eager to connect and explore how you can work together.
                  </p>

                  <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="width: 33.33%; padding: 10px;">
                        <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; height: 100%;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 600;">Phone</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #111827; font-weight: 600;">{{advisorPhone}}</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 12px;">
                            <a href="{{advisorTelHref}}" style="color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none;">Call {{advisorCompanyName}}</a>
                          </p>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td style="width: 33.33%; padding: 10px;">
                        <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; height: 100%;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 600;">Email</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #111827; font-weight: 600; word-break: break-all;">{{advisorEmail}}</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 12px;">
                            <a href="{{advisorEmailHref}}" style="color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none;">Email {{advisorCompanyName}}</a>
                          </p>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td style="width: 33.33%; padding: 10px;">
                        <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; height: 100%;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 600;">Website</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; word-break: break-all;">
                            <a href="{{advisorWebsiteHref}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none;">{{advisorWebsiteText}}</a>
                          </p>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="width: 50%; padding: 10px;">
                        <div style="background-color: #eef2ff; border: 1px solid #c7d2fe; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; height: 100%;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #4338ca; font-weight: 700;">Focus Industries</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.5;">{{advisorIndustries}}</p>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td style="width: 50%; padding: 10px;">
                        <div style="background-color: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; height: 100%;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #047857; font-weight: 700;">Geographic Coverage</p>
                          <p style="margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.5;">{{advisorGeographies}}</p>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <div style="background-color: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="vertical-align: top;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #047857; font-weight: 700;">Typical Client Revenue</p>
                          <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 18px; color: #065f46; font-weight: 700;">{{advisorRevenueRange}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td style="text-align: right; vertical-align: middle;">
                          <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background-color: #d1fae5; color: #047857; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Aligned Opportunity</span>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;">
                    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 18px; color: #111827;">About {{advisorCompanyName}}</h2>
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #1f2937;">{{advisorDescription}}</p>
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6366f1; font-weight: 700;">Seller Snapshot</p>
                    <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #111827;">{{sellerCompany}}</h3>
                    <p style="margin: 6px 0 12px; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563;">Industry: {{sellerIndustry}} · Location: {{sellerGeography}}</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.6;">{{sellerDescription}}</p>
                    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 12px;">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="width: 50%; padding: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563;">Annual revenue</td>
                        <td style="width: 50%; padding: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #111827; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;">${{sellerRevenue}}</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="width: 50%; padding: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563;">Primary contact</td>
                        <td style="width: 50%; padding: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #111827; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;">{{sellerName}} · {{sellerEmail}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </div>

                  <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; font-weight: 600;">Recommended next steps</p>
                    <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li>Reply to this email to start the conversation.</li>
                      <li>Share availability for an introductory call with {{sellerName}}.</li>
                      <li>Review the opportunity details on your dashboard for additional context.</li>
                    </ol>
                  </div>

                  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                    <a href="{{AdvisordashboardUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed); color: #ffffff; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Open Advisor Dashboard</a>
                  </div>

                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">Need help? Reach out to support@advisorchooser.com</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p style="margin: 24px auto 0; max-width: 680px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        You are receiving this introduction because the seller selected you on the Advisor Chooser Platform. Use the contact details above to reply directly to the seller.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
